Welcome to Acedia! Whether it's
sightseeing or shopping you're
after, Acedia has it all.

rows.label: tlk46300077_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Superbia and Invidia have
brokered a ceasefire...
But the refugees remain.

rows.label: tlk46300077_03_msg0003
rows.name:
The war's not over until these
people get to return home.

rows.label: tlk46300077_03_msg0004
rows.name:
But who knows when that'll
happen. Or even if it ever will.
